#: ../../I/interrupt.rst:5
msgid "interrupt"
msgstr "interrupt"

#: ../../I/interrupt.rst:8
msgid ""
"[techspeak] n. On a computer, an event that interrupts normal processing and"
" temporarily diverts flow-of-control through an \"interrupt handler\" "
"routine. See also :ref:`trap`\\."
msgstr ""
"[テックスピーク] 名詞。コンピュータ上で、通常の処理を中断し、「割り込みハンドラ」ルーチンを通じて制御の流れを一時的に逸らすイベント。\\ "
":ref:`trap`\\ も参照。"

#: ../../I/interrupt.rst:11
msgid ""
"interj. A request for attention from a hacker. Often explicitly spoken. "
"\"Interrupt — have you seen Joe recently?\" See :ref:`priority-interrupt`\\."
msgstr ""
"間投詞。ハッカーからの注意の要求。しばしば明示的に口に出される。「Interrupt — 最近Joeを見たかい?」\\ :ref:`priority-"
"interrupt`\\ を参照。"
